title: Mariners of the Sky (1936) WILLIAM GARGAN

sources.title: Mariners of the Sky (1936) WILLIAM GARGAN
sources.description:
Stars: William Gargan, Claire Dodd, Douglas Fowley
Director: Nate Watt

A touching story of a naval officer who adopts a boy who is orphaned when his parents are tragically killed. (a.k.a. Navy Born)
